de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.job

Enum JobStartingStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<JobStartingStrategy>
      • de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.job.JobStartingStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<JobStartingStrategy>

    public enum JobStartingStrategy
extends java.lang.Enum<JobStartingStrategy>
    Strategies for handling jobs that want to wait for other jobs to be finished first.
    Possible strategies:
     RETURN
 WAIT
 WAIT_ONE
 CANCEL_WAIT
 CANCEL_WAIT_ONE
    Author:
    Sebastian Krieter

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CANCEL_WAIT
      Same as WAIT, but attempts to cancel all previous jobs.
      CANCEL_WAIT_ONE
      Same as WAIT_ONE, but attempts to cancel all previous jobs.
      RETURN
      If another job is already running the given job is not started.
      WAIT
      Waits for all other jobs to finish.
      WAIT_ONE
      Waits for another job to finish, except a third job is already waiting.
